{"tid":1787679,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"分享去暗瘡的個人經驗","createTime":"2019-12-18T06:02:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T12:43:16.000Z","uid":234808,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f1aee624ea2e3f3f4aa4f9cab6eb336b10c2d212","tid":1787679,"uid":234808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T06:02:16.000Z","msg":"本人有一兩年因為壓力等因素生左好多暗瘡  但卒之用了以下方法已經好耐無生<br />\n<br />\n1. 每朝起身 只用溫水洗面 唔用任何洗面奶<br />\n2. 覺得皮膚乾嘅時候 會適量食啲煎炸野分泌出油分  <br />\n     等塊面冇咁乾<br />\n3. 覺得火氣盛嘅時候會飲一兩罐啤酒降火<br />\n4. 得閒會食譚仔三小辣 因為食少少辣可幫助排毒<br />\n5. 間唔中會飲下雞骨草（或中藥）幫助清走體濕熱        <br />\n    確保排便正常<br />\n6. 不用任何護膚品 只用一隻德國牌子的洋甘菊酒精 （萬寧有得賣 ）去塗少少消毒一下暗瘡流血位置<br />\n7. 就算塊面生到痴線都唔好必啲暗蒼 因為一定留痕<br />\n8. 盡量唔好俾自己有太大壓力<br />\n<br />\n（只供參考）"},{"pid":"61ab72d07aacf2a015eb6c030bd95bb507135a0f","tid":1787679,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T12:40:58.000Z","msg":"用the ordinary 產品ko"},{"pid":"6d72512825b2d873462c544c2b1df1f4d9abd6b6","tid":1787679,"uid":38891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T12:41:52.000Z","msg":"oxy5 幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fce03e4555b1737687ba16af86284ca0979b22b9","tid":1787679,"uid":3764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"61ab72d07aacf2a015eb6c030bd95bb507135a0f","tid":1787679,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T12:40:58.000Z","msg":"用the ordinary 產品ko"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T12:42:21.000Z","msg":"用咗邊隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"928412130a6957297ffefddba0ca373118566875","tid":1787679,"uid":335063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T12:43:15.000Z","msg":"唔好用毛巾印臉 多細菌"},{"pid":"8e39dcbaba7d9443cc6dbbbe969a5c318e68f52d","tid":1787679,"uid":132587,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T12:43:16.000Z","msg":"睇到2 3 4果陣覺得你係靠害<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.